lead_paragraph: Kraigg Brathwaite carried his bat for an unbeaten 142 to put West Indies in a strong position to beat Pakistan in the third and final test in Sharjah on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Unbeaten Brathwaite Gives Windies Hope of Consolation Win
